<br>
Instead of camping the jboots, find a necro with the ring and sacrifice down to the beginning of 49 and sell him the essence stones for completion of the ring quest.<br>
<br>
Time to make 5 bubbles in lvl 49: 6-7 hrs<br>
Time to camp the AC: up to 36 hrs.<br>
<br>
/e shines his jboots.<br>
<br>
I am already back to 50 and have my eye on an SMR. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uezno.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ezno</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/posticons/eyes.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 190<br> <font color=#333333>(10/12/00 7:36:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=77.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Dont camp!  Kill!</span><hr size=1> <br>
