<br>
The player must be 46+ (planes capible) to be sacrificed.<br>
When sacrificed, you die. You can't be rezzed. (side note - I heard of a 56 rouge that decided to stop playing EQ. She had a necro friend....so she let herself be sacrificed over and over till she lost 46)<br>
The Necro gets the gem after you die, not you.<br>
The gem is used for 3 high level necro spells. They are:<br>
<br>
Convergence, a level 53 spell that acts like a cleric rez, and restores 93% exp.<br>
<br>
Infusion, a level 55 spell that gives the necro 1000 mana. Casting time of 3 seconds, so it's set up like an emergency spell.<br>
